ers:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Get a rising challenge of difficulty on the final puzzles. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Solve the puzzles under a certain amount of moves and collect all the Golden Socks!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269830/extras/40c7808522f50e61ea977b259d8de08d.poster.avif?t=1593281167\" width=596 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269830/extras/40c7808522f50e61ea977b259d8de08d.webm?t=1593281167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269830/extras/40c7808522f50e61ea977b259d8de08d.mp4?t=1593281167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269830/extras/2ba1b9b40f6f59f9b5e06385e4d8995e.avif?t=1593281167\" width=600 height=121 /></span>",
